summary:
This mod adds in the following; Bronze Ingots, Nordic Boots, Nordic Gauntlets, Nordic Cuirass, Nordic Helment, Nordic Mask, Ultimate Nordic Mask.
All of which are enchantable, Bronze Ingots can be bought at any Blacksmith.
